Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:45.44,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Konačno je na redu Ruin koncert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.29,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Biće u redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:55.24,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,667)}Sigurna sam da će nam Čiaki i Rui prirediti izvanredno izvođenje koje će zadovoljiti sve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.33,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ali sigurna sam da neće ličiti na ono što bih ja želela da izvodim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:03.26,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ionako ovo delo uopšte ne odgovara njima dvoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:07.45,nodame,kuroki,0000,0000,0000,,M-Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.06,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Biće u redu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:14.98,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Pre neki dan sam pomenula da mogu da učim i bez direktnih iskustava...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.99,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,...ali sada sam uzbuđena zbog ovog novog iskustva.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.58,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Novog? Kako to misliš?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.65,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,To je tajna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:27.68,nodame,man,0000,0000,0000,,Vreme je.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:29.24,nodame,man,0000,0000,0000,,Izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:32.11,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Iznenada se osećam nervozno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:36.94,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(3102,3268,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&\4c&HF7F7F7&)}Vreme je da se malo zabavimo uz muziku.{season 1, episode 10 @ 21:06}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:42.16,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Onda kada sam imao toliko briga,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.95,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(3130,3797,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&\4c&HF7F7F7&)}Štrezeman me je spasao muzikom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.50,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Rui...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.44,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćemo li?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:37.54,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Obožavam današnju publiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.66,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Ovo delo me podseća na Nodame.{season 3, episode 7 @ 18:55}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.42,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Završilo se.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:54.03,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,420)}Ljubav je stvarno jako zabavna,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.88,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,ali je pomalo i bolna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.91,nodame,mom,0000,0000,0000,,I ja sam toliko uživala, Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.32,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.66,nodame,rui,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, već se završilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.32,nodame,tanya,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame, hoćeš li do toaleta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.54,nodame,tanya,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.03,nodame,yun,0000,0000,0000,,Bio je to dobar koncert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.35,nodame,frank,0000,0000,0000,,Baš je bio zabavan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.32,nodame,tanya,0000,0000,0000,,I uzbudljiv!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.70,nodame,frank,0000,0000,0000,,Ruin karakter se nekako izmenio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:31.53,nodame,tanya,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, nisam znala da može da postigne takav veseo i otvoren zvuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.78,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Možda zato što je bila sa Čiakijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.90,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Sa njime je lako sarađivati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:40.47,nodame,frank,0000,0000,0000,,Luka, postaješ sve mračniji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.17,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,I ja želim to da radim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.84,nodame,tanya,0000,0000,0000,,Šta to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:46.63,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Da dirigujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.92,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Možda bih i ja mogao da se oprobam u tome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.97,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Onda ću možda jednog dana moći da izvodim sa Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.77,nodame,lucas,0000,0000,0000,,Čekaj, Nodame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.34,nodame,tanya,0000,0000,0000,,Već neko vreme nije sa nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:58.81,nodame,yun,0000,0000,0000,,Nisi izabrao dobar trenutak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.50,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Bilo je to dobro izvođenje.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:11.90,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Drago mi je što je Rui uspela da priredi onakvo izvođenje,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:18.16,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,a osećaj rastuće tenzije u publici koji sam mogao da osetim iza sebe je bio neverovatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.73,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Pitam se kako se Nodame osećala?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:26.44,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ona se uvek ponaša impulsivno kada je Rui u pitanju.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.31,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,I ja želim da sviram kao ti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:35.20,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,871)}Sviraću na koncertu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:36.98,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:39.04,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nadam se da ovaj put nije tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.97,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Želim da je ovo motiviše na dobar način.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.65,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrodošao kući, Čiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.72,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zašto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.23,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mogla si da dođeš da me posetiš u svlačionici.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.87,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nekako sam se tek u zadnji trenutak setila toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:01.13,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Večerašnji koncert je bio jako dobar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.33,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,I ti i Rui ste bili dobri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.29,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.17,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Bila sam iznenađena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:11.76,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Mislila sam da ćeš izvoditi više nadmeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:16.03,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Osećaj "zabavnosti" je bio neverovatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.72,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kako to misliš, "da izvodim nadmeno"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.71,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,U svakom slučaju, hajde, sedi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.26,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Sigurno si umoran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.02,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćeš li prvo večeru, ili da se okupaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.61,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ili možda mene?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:30.69,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Onda—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.77,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Tako je!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:34.62,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ovo je prilika za šampanjac!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.96,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro-obavljeno žurka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:36.68,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.96,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ja ću spremiti neke grickalice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.18,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,a ti idi, okupaj se prvo, ili tako nešto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.66,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.63,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Puririn Gorota, Puri Gorota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.63,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Šta, bre...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.69,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Je li se ikada ponašala ovako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.27,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ova reakcija je...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.57,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,...bez presedana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.11,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Živeli!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.57,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Čestitam na uspešnom izvođenju.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.00,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:31.21,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Mogu li večeras da ostanem ovde, Šiniči?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.17,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,M-Možeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:38.27,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ali sutra ponovo putujem za Italiju, pa ustajem rano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.64,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Opet ideš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.38,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,I ja želim da idem u Italiju!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.48,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Karbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:49.64,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,A želim i da upoznam maestra Vieru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.98,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Kada ćeš da me predstaviš njemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.79,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Predstavim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.44,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, videćemo jednom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:59.44,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ali pusti to, zar nemaš ti ispite uskoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.06,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kako ti ide sa učenjem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.88,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Koliko si napredovala sa svojim lekcijama od onda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.53,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Jesi li završila Betovena?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:10.07,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Napredujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:14.05,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Više nema potrebe da se brineš oko toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.53,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kakav ti je to čudan ton glasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.59,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I nemoj da skrećeš pogled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.47,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ako je stvarno sve u redu, gledaj me u oči dok pričaš!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.93,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ipak se ponaša čudno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.93,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Koji je pravi razlog što si došla ovde?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:36.28,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Čiaki, voliš li me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.64,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:41.17,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Bićemo zauvek zajedno, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.07,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zašto me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:49.59,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ne znam šta se dešava,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:57.17,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,ali sigurno pokušava da se izbori sa nečime, na na neki njoj svojstven, uvrnut način.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.29,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sigurno je tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:35.46,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Noda—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.71,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Čiaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:41.97,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Venčajmo se. {ovaj deo se koristi u kasnijim epizodama}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.50,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,B-Budalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.83,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nemoj da buncaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.22,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Pa, ja odoh sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.16,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ne zaboravi da zaključaš kada kreneš.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.58,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zvaću te.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.78,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je to bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:19.00,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zavitlavala se, kao i obično?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.09,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uvek tvrdi da mi je supruga...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:22.57,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.02,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Pogledala me je pravo u oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.90,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Son Rui procvetala u Parizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:38.68,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Drsko izvođenje Viltord orkestra izrazilo je na blistav i skladan način
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:43.64,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,nevinost jednog mladog srca isprepletenu sa zrelošću koja ga obuhvata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.79,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Rui, koja je patila od pritiska zbog njenog statusa genija,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:53.29,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,prihvativši sebe je povratila svoju ljubav prema muzici i neograničene mogućnosti koje su pred njom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:13:00.58,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Šiniči Čiaki, mladi dirigent koji joj je pružao podršku, je još jedna buduća nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.01,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Čiakija su pomenuli u samo jednoj rečenici!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:10.68,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Danas ću sa Šiniči Čiakijem ići kod "Još jednog poljupca"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.85,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.81,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Kakva sreća da te nađem ovde!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.52,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde opet zajedno da se zabavimo kod "Još jednog poljupca"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.95,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Ili hoćeš da napravimo izložbu kupaćih kostima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.53,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.70,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.54,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Jesi li se posvađala sa Čiakijem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.50,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Pobegla si od kuće?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.23,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:43.28,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Ako želiš tako, možeš da se isplačeš na mojim grudima!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.97,nodame,auclair,0000,0000,0000,,Noda Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:59.56,nodame,auclair,0000,0000,0000,,Još malo pa će tri godine od kako je došla u Pariz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.21,nodame,auclair,0000,0000,0000,,Ovo je prvi put da je odsutna sa časa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.14,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Čiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.28,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Šta je bilo, Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.97,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Da nisi raskinula sa Čiakijem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.88,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Ionako ste opet počeli da živite razdvojeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.43,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Nije tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.27,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Zaprosila sam ga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.48,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,A on je mislio da se šalim i samo me je ignorisao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.20,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Želiš da se venčaš, Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.97,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.50,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Da nisi trudna?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.18,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Nije tako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.53,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Nisam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:58.35,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ni sama ne znam zašto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.75,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Zašto sam to rekla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:08.84,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Jednostavno sam više umorna... od akademije i od klavira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.43,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.62,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Koju želiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:19.82,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Žan, niste morali da počnete da se kartate čim je došao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.03,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Vodi me u kupovinu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.07,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Znam, Juko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.56,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Idemo posle ove partije.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.53,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde, izvoli, Čiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.97,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Žane, to je previše očigledno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.83,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Čiaki, da ti nije loše?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.97,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Danas se ceo dan ponašaš čudno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.44,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Zamislio si se i puštaš Žana da ti radi šta hoće.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.14,nodame,yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Da nemaš temperaturu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.30,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.85,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Da li da je pozovem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:53.78,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.99,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1520,1687,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&\4c&HF7F7F7&)}Venčajmo se.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.79,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Šta da radim ako je bila ozbiljna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.64,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:09.20,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Zapravo, tada sam na trenutak pomislio "Ah... ponovo beži."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.84,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.80,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Želeo sam da mislim da je to šala.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.49,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do vraga! Kakav sam kreten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:20.13,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Šta?! Već je gotovo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.16,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Ali imao si džokera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.46,nodame,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Idem da bacim pogled na probu opere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.88,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Tako znači.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:33.77,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Čiaki i Rui su izvodili ono što si ti želela.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.34,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Pa više nemaš motivacije.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.13,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.38,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Oni su učinili i više nego što sam ja želela da učinim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.04,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,To nije bilo samo nešto posebno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.19,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Bilo je jako posebno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.90,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Više nije bitno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.25,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ne moram to da budem ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:56.78,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Čiaki, i svi ostali...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.55,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Koliko god žele...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.94,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,To je čudno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:04.72,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Ako je bilo tako dobro, trebala bi da budeš motivisana da učiniš nešto još bolje.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.08,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ne mogu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:10.05,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Nećeš moći da nastaviš u suprotnom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.65,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ionako ni ne mogu da nastavim dalje.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.72,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Znači i u Parizu zaostaješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.83,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ne zaostajem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.87,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Učila sam kako treba,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.08,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,i svim srcem sam se posvetila muzici!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.02,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Ali... šta onda?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:32.57,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Rui je to najnormalnije radila još od malih nogu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.47,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,I Čiaki takođe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:39.57,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Znam da bih trebala da nastavim još da se trudim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.54,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Znam to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:48.25,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde da čujem kako sviraš klavir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.50,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Kada razmislim, nisam čuo kako sviraš još od Japana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:57.68,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćeš li da mi pokažeš rezultate tvog studiranja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:02.24,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćemo li se ovde rastati, ili...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.29,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Poslednji put...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.15,nodame,nodame,0000,0000,0000,,Dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.65,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Pesma tugovanja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.24,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Savladan zamorom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.10,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,...ne možeš više da misliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:43.24,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Nećeš da sviraš fugu na kraju?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.53,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Ispunjenu radošću.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.06,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:56.15,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,zar ne želiš da saznaš koliko je zabavno kada se posvetiš muzici svim srcem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.07,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćeš li opet pobeći?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.82,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ali zašto sada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.89,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kada si toliko daleko stigla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.81,nodame,chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,To nije ispravno, Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:21.74,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,"Budem li ti znao ugoditi, biću ti sluga, rob, što budeš hteo!"{Mephistopheles - Faust, Part 1 Scene 4}{strana 45}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.18,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Postoji nešto što si želela da učiniš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.72,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Zar ne želiš bar jednom da probaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:34.17,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Hoćeš li da zaboraviš na Čiakija i pođeš sa mnom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:43.54,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,"Ja ću na ovom, svetu tebi služiti, bez počinka i stanka što god ti srce želi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.14,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,"A kad na onom opet budemo se sreli..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.28,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,"ti ćeš se meni..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:11.74,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,"istim tim..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.92,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,"...odužiti."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.63,nodame,stresemann,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.39,nodame,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sam Noda Megumi, 20, iz Tokija.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:53.70,nodame,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Završila sam Momogaoka akademiju i parisku muzičku akademiju sa najboljim ocenama u odeljenju.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:55.55,nodame,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Sve laži!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,nodame,preview,0000,0000,0000,,{indeed, she is 25, from Saga prefecture, dropped out from Momogaoka, and has not graduated from Conservatoire yet.}
